I would like the ability to Manually Set the Estimated Burndown Goal of a Sprint

What I mean by this is If I know that the team's goal is 150 pts I would simply like to enter 150 for a sprint and that would be its starting point and burndown from there. Even if I had 120 story pts worth of cards it would still start burning down from 150.

Currently, it calculates its starting point by adding all the cards story pts at the beginning of a sprint. Also currently if I delete a card that was included in calculating the initial burndown value that value then drops by the amount that was the card I deleted.

